 />\n<br />\n統治勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢搶首都<br />\n宗教勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢傳教<br />\n文化勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢發展旅遊<br />\n科技勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢射火箭上太空</blockquote><br />\n我次次都係唔起兵 然後個城唔夠位起屋 之後科技領先再畀人打爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bc898fde601476809047e16e467a8a7ebaaa67","tid":28081,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"蠻族6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639273c725bdeb48aadc0c50a6310302a60a7b33","tid":28081,"uid":21706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"好耐無開尋晚玩左場<br />\n<br />\n發覺斬樹只可以斬勢力範圍內<br />\n<br />\n無得再好似以前咁斬到老練咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即刻唔識玩"},{"pid":"4bb49472041e735579fd4ba9f180d9ee8c31d795","tid":28081,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蠻族6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小朋友齊打交6 呢隻根本戰爭game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d72a0a7df68f038eb042f902adbe6cdbc37276b","tid":28081,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:41:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日想和平地玩都比人搞<br />\n迫住玩野蠻帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n統治勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢搶首都<br />\n宗教勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢傳教<br />\n文化勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢發展旅遊<br />\n科技勝利：狂起兵打殘電腦再慢慢射火箭上太空</blockquote><br />\n我次次都係唔起兵 然後個城唔夠位起屋 之後科技領先再畀人打爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宗教狗真係好可恥"},{"pid":"3981d1b6d3225b02c58a8cdd07ab8b15a5e6da89","tid":28081,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-